  Purpose :    Local SVC to turn ON/OFF the authorized mode, or to get
  ---------    some TIME values requests.

  How used :   only through the assembler macros SETAUTH, RESAUTH and
  ----------   $TREQ.

  SVC number : replace the characters ### by the selected SVC number
  ------------ in the AUTHSVC source, the AUTHSVC$ JCL and the macros
               SETAUTH/RESAUTH/$TREQ.
